profile:
GIT R DONE Property Maintenance 
We are a full service property maintenance business that specializes in landscaping and snow removal.
We offer weekly and monthly services.
Weekly & Bi Weekly Lawn Cutting Services:
- Professional grass cutting
- Edging/ trimming of walkways, flower beds, etc.
- Removal of grass clippings from walkways, driveways, patios, etc.
Fall Yard Clean Up:
- Raking & Collecting Leaves
- Pruning shrubs & hedges
- Final lawn mowing of year
Eavestrough Cleaning:
- Clean out blocked gutters & downspouts to direct water away from home.
Snow Removal Services:
- Season or monthly billing, contracts, & one time clearings all available
- Residential only
- Snow blowers & shovels 
- FULLY INSURED !!!!!!
***(please make arrangements prior to snowfall to ensure removal within 12 hours after snowfall . Thank you)***
Spring Yard Clean Up:
- Raking & collecting leaves
- Edging & turning garden beds
- Shrub/ hedge trimming
- First lawn mowing of year
Junk/Scrap removal:
-free e-waste and scrap metal pick up and removal
- residential, apartment, house, Garbage, Yard waste , Garage clean outs, trash left behind by tenants, foreclosures, backyard clean ups.. And much more
Contact us today for a free estimate on any of our services
We Git "R" Done Call Jamie: 519 774 2223.
